edu.colorado.cs.ngn.lime

Class LimeContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.colorado.cs.ngn.lime.LimeContainer

  • public class LimeContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    Keep track of created instances of switches and their info Original Switches: include switches that OF controller always see Active Switches: include actual switches in the network and they map to Original Switches. Must be the same number as Original Switches Cloned Switches: include switches to be cloned to. every cloned switches must map to one active switch. Number of Cloned switches <= Active Switches Working Switches: include active and cloned switches Slicer Switches: Switches that talk with controller. Must be the same number as original switches
    Author:
    Murad Kaplan
